data.description: Davenport Townhome Style Condo For Sale! Move right in and enjoy this, "Easy Living Lifestyle."  This home features an Open Floorplan, 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, 2 Half Bathrooms, Upper-Level Laundry Room, Deck entrance from great room, and attached garage.  For your convenience all of the kitchen appliances stay. Check out the Finished Basement that features Bedroom/Den, w/ Egress Window, New Carpet, Storage and Newly completed Bathroom.  Call for your personal showing today!
